short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Local google to search your bookmarks

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
The amount of new content you come across everyday is overwhelming, the internet moves so fast that it's very hard to find again something you saw or some reference you need, even on Google.

Cataloger brings a different usage for your bookmarks: instead of just the websites you access the most, you can bookmark any page you find interesting and may want to remember or use as reference later. No need to manually organize them because the search is very effective, now you can access any documents and articles in a heartbeat, and build your personal search engine.
